Comment: 10,0:18:41.30,0:18:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Comment: 10,0:18:43.51,0:18:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Little sis!
Comment: 10,0:18:48.30,0:18:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Comment: 10,0:18:50.15,0:18:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, only got one. Wonder if my trap broke.
Comment: 10,0:18:58.86,0:19:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Poaching. Bad! Got it? {this is likely a reference to babymetal's ijime. zettai. dame. }
Comment: 10,0:19:01.60,0:19:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Comment: 10,0:19:09.25,0:19:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hurry! Hurry! Hurry! Hurry! Hurry! Hurry! Hurry! Hurry!
Comment: 10,0:19:14.34,0:19:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it...
Comment: 10,0:19:26.18,0:19:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Ursula, you were supposed to be with her.
Comment: 10,0:19:28.92,0:19:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Comment: 10,0:19:30.56,0:19:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You even put Professor Pisces in grave danger.
Comment: 10,0:19:35.57,0:19:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Pisces says it was fun to be able to swim around in a large lake after all this time.
Comment: 10,0:19:41.57,0:19:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that is quite correct.
Comment: 10,0:19:44.30,0:19:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She also says you've received\Nan A in magic philosophy.
Comment: 10,0:19:47.54,0:19:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You impressed her by putting what you learned in class into practice of your own volition.
Comment: 10,0:19:51.96,0:19:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko, you can understand fish language?
Comment: 10,0:19:53.92,0:19:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I guess so.
Comment: 10,0:19:55.46,0:19:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That is no excuse!
Comment: 10,0:19:57.09,0:19:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot overlook what you have done.
Comment: 10,0:19:59.34,0:20:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"Merman sighted at the lake"?
Comment: 10,0:20:01.84,0:20:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! From back then?! {apparently some time passed}
Comment: 10,0:20:04.01,0:20:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Miss Kagari? {I think this was our standard...}{## for english speakers, yeah}
Comment: 10,0:20:05.57,0:20:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Our school has never been this shamed since its founding!
Comment: 10,0:20:08.25,0:20:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I request the expulsion of Atsuko Kagari on grounds of disgracing the dignity of our academy!
Comment: 10,0:20:14.23,0:20:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Comment: 10,0:20:15.69,0:20:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You may see Miss Kagari as just a poor student unable to use magic if you compare her to her classmates.{she's just a poor girl, from a japanese family. also you don't technically need to separate these phrases}
Comment: 10,0:20:22.20,0:20:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But she has learned to understand fish language,\Nand although she has yet to master it,
Comment: 10,0:20:27.33,0:20:31.12,Default,,15,15,0,,she's continuously improving her metamorphosis magic!
Comment: 10,0:20:31.12,0:20:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You should not be comparing her to other students, but to how she was on the day of her enrollment!
Comment: 10,0:20:35.45,0:20:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody can deny that she's continuing to grow through her failures!
Comment: 10,0:20:38.71,0:20:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She has absolutely no value as a witch.
Comment: 10,0:20:41.92,0:20:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Should you not be appraising how she is unable to ignore those suffering before her,
Comment: 10,0:20:46.22,0:20:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,putting their feelings above her own desires?!
Comment: 10,0:20:50.20,0:20:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting grades or outward appearances above that...
Comment: 10,0:20:53.38,0:20:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is pure foolishness!
Comment: 10,0:20:56.61,0:20:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}I{\i0} approve of her!
Comment: 10,0:21:08.49,0:21:13.44,Default,,0,0,40,,{\an8}Pardon me, Headmistress. We've received an incomprehensible phone call.
Comment: 10,0:21:13.44,0:21:15.92,Default,,15,15,40,,{\an8}They're asking if the merman is a student of Luna Nova.
Comment: 10,0:21:15.92,0:21:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You see now?
Comment: 10,0:21:17.58,0:21:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is on the line?
Comment: 10,0:21:18.88,0:21:20.94,Default,,0,0,40,,{\an8}It's the Environmental Agency.
Comment: 10,0:21:20.94,0:21:25.84,Default,,0,0,40,,{\an8}They wish to commend the merman who saved an endangered species of fish from poaching.{this is all to see finneran's smirk}
Comment: 10,0:21:26.80,0:21:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess those fish were endangered.
Comment: 10,0:21:29.84,0:21:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell them that the merman was one of ours.
Comment: 10,0:21:32.77,0:21:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust you're fine with that, Professor Finneran.
Comment: 10,0:21:35.78,0:21:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What about her expulsion?
Comment: 10,0:21:37.23,0:21:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,One of our students is receiving a public commendation.
Comment: 10,0:21:40.03,0:21:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree we should keep her here with us, Miss Merman?
Comment: 10,0:21:43.39,0:21:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saved...
Comment: 10,0:21:45.11,0:21:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great, Akko!
Comment: 10,0:21:46.99,0:21:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,However, we cannot ignore how you\Nattempted to cheat on your exam.
Comment: 10,0:21:50.77,0:21:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be punished for that.
Comment: 10,0:21:53.44,0:21:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How does this sound?
Comment: 10,0:21:57.54,0:22:03.88,Default,,15,15,0,,For the next week, we will share mealtimes and nighttimes as I drill the expectations of a witch into you.{## sleep together, eeeeh}
Comment: 10,0:22:03.88,0:22:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,First, as per the rules, we will retire at nine o'clock!{## i'd rather lose the very american PM; this should be understandable enough to not mention "evening"}
Comment: 10,0:22:06.22,0:22:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we wake at four! Keep in mind that a filthy room houses a filthy soul.
Comment: 10,0:22:09.39,0:22:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Always keep it clean!
Comment: 10,0:22:10.88,0:22:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I get roped in?
Comment: 10,0:22:12.58,0:22:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Ursula, I didn't know that's how you thought about me.
Comment: 10,0:22:17.04,0:22:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You really sounded like a teacher.
Comment: 10,0:22:19.40,0:22:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Comment: 10,0:22:20.56,0:22:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but I {\fax-0.2}am{\i0} a teacher!
Comment: 10,0:22:22.73,0:22:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You two! Move your hands, not your mouths!
Comment: 10,0:22:25.60,0:22:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
